metadata.name: Trapped
metadata.description:
Do we need to escape from distractions or we are searching for distractions in our everyday life? 
Making woman look like cyborg represents our everyday routine .. wake up, coffee, shower, breakfast, work etc. like following some program. And there are times when you feel like want to escape from it all .. beach and cocktail sounds good, but can your mind be able to escape? ..we are being trapped in our own windless space inside our head.
